<h3 id="highest-resolution-video-of-pete-seeger-playing-this-that-ive-found">Highest resolution video of Pete Seeger playing this that I’ve found</h3>
<p>It looks like he is playing capo 6, in drop-D, using the chords D-G-A. However, to my ear, it sounds like he’s playing A-D-E (with capo 6). Either way, it’s nice we have this video!</p>
